# Data Dictionary and Visualizer

The visualizer displays only what is in the **data dictionary** (`facility-summary-mvp/output/data-dictionary/data-dictionary.json`). Tables/fields that exist in DDL but not in this file will not appear.

- **Compare (report):** `node scripts/compare-ddl-to-datadict.mjs` — L1/L2/L3 DDL vs data dictionary; lists missing tables/columns.
- **Sync (add missing):** `node scripts/augment-datadict-from-ddl.mjs` — adds missing tables/columns from DDL into the data dictionary.
- DDL sources: L1 `scripts/l1/output/ddl.sql`, L2 `scripts/l2/output/ddl.sql`, L3 `sql/l3/01_DDL_all_tables.sql`.

See `docs/DATA_DICTIONARY_VISUALIZER.md` for full notes.
